%N A139821 Triangle T(i,j) read by rows: T(i,1) = Fibonacci(i) for all i; T(i,i) = i for all i; T(i,j) = T(i-1,j) + T(i-2,j) + T(i-1,j-1) - T(i-2,j-1).
